channel.title: [PI] 317 -- Jar Client Help! --
channel.description:
Well, obviously. I am a noob compared to most of you.
So, I'm asking how do I jar this Client? It's Project Insanity, and i'm using JAR MAKER, i'm filling in the details correctly, and manifest template: Main Class is: client
I tried, capital Client, didn't work, lower-cased client, didn't work.
I ran through my client files, client.class, meaning it should be lower-cased.
I tried to jar with .java files, and with just .class files.
Here is what my client looks like: With .java files:
1ST HALF OF CLIENT .java FILES: [url=http://prntscr.com/53s2vk]http://prntscr.com/53s2vk[/url] 2ND HALF OF CLIENT .java FILES: [url=http://prntscr.com/53s3kz]http://prntscr.com/53s3kz[/url] 3RD HALF OF CLIENT .java FILES: [url=http://prntscr.com/53s3wu]http://prntscr.com/53s3wu[/url] LAST HALF OF CLIENT .java FILES: [url=http://prntscr.com/53s46d]http://prntscr.com/53s46d[/url]
I appreciate any help, and please. Do not tell me not to use this source or anything like that. I want to learn, and whilst learning, you make mistakes. Don't tell me otherwise.
Last thing to imply, I am using this source/client: [url=http://www.runelocus.com/forums/showthread.php?102708-Rsps-2007scape]http://www.runelocus.com/forums/showthread.php?102708-Rsps-2007scape[/url]
rune^^locus Thanks.
